annotation.table_summary: This table presents Apple Inc.'s consolidated statements of operations for the fiscal years ended September 27, 2025, September 28, 2024, and September 30, 2023, showing revenue, expenses, and profitability metrics.

row_summaries.description: This row shows the net sales from Apple's product category for each fiscal year.
This row shows the net sales from Apple's services category for each fiscal year.
This row shows the combined net sales from both products and services for each fiscal year.
This row shows the cost of sales for Apple's product category for each fiscal year.
This row shows the cost of sales for Apple's services category for each fiscal year.
This row shows the combined cost of sales for both products and services for each fiscal year.
This row shows the gross margin, which is the difference between net sales and cost of sales, for each fiscal year.
This row shows Apple's research and development expenses for each fiscal year.
This row shows Apple's selling, general and administrative expenses for each fiscal year.
This row shows the combined operating expenses for each fiscal year.
This row shows Apple's operating income for each fiscal year.
This row shows other income or expense, net, for each fiscal year.

row_summaries.row_label: Income before provision for income taxes
row_summaries.description: This row shows Apple's income before provision for income taxes for each fiscal year.
This row shows Apple's provision for income taxes for each fiscal year.
This row shows Apple's net income for each fiscal year.
This row shows Apple's basic earnings per share for each fiscal year.
This row shows Apple's diluted earnings per share for each fiscal year.
This row shows the number of shares used in computing basic earnings per share for each fiscal year.
This row shows the number of shares used in computing diluted earnings per share for each fiscal year.
